      "rationale": "The validation constructs are production-representative 7.5 mm non-cannulated pedicle screws of the same design as those in the COU. The ASTM F1717 test configuration used in validation is identical to the configuration for which the FEA model will be used in the regulatory submission. The validation domain fully overlaps the COU prediction domain. Gradation 3 achieved."
